            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your<strong> chopped tomatoes</strong> and<strong> halved cherry tomatoes</strong> to the pan and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Add the <strong>chicken</strong> <strong>stock</strong> a ladle at a time, stirring continuously for 25-30 min or until all of the stock is absorbed and the rice is almost cooked</p>",
