            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the rice is almost cooked, add the <strong>shredded kale</strong> to the pan with a small splash of <strong>water</strong> and stir everything together until wilted</p><p>Add a knob of <strong>butter</strong>, a generous grind of <strong>black pepper</strong> and<strong> half</strong> of the <strong>grated Italian hard cheese </strong>(save the rest for garnish!)</p><p>Give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>tomato risotto</strong></p>",
